OL,4,Chas 'partitionist' stance on tuition
OL,5,Cfees
OL,7,FSinn Fein's Economy minister has
OL,8,Frejected claims her party is adopting
OL,9,Fa "partitionist" approach to student
OL,10,Ffees after she declined to rule out an
OL,11,Fincrease north of the border.
OL,13,FCaoimhe Archibald said ideally
OL,14,Fstudents would not have to pay any
OL,15,Ffees in Northern Ireland but added
OL,16,Fthat the Executive has to work within
OL,17,F"financial reality" as she blamed the
OL,18,FUK Government for "imposing" a fee-
OL,19,Fbased system in the region.
