OL,5,Cfees
OL,7,FLast week, university chiefs in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland jointly called on
OL,9,Fpolitical leaders to back a
OL,10,Fsignificant increase in tuition fees,
OL,11,Fwarning that failure to tackle a
OL,12,Ffunding crisis in the sector will
OL,13,Fforce them to cut places for local
OL,14,Fstudents.
OL,16,FMs Archibald's comments to the
OL,17,FAssembly on Tuesday came after SDLP
OL,18,FMLA Sinead McLaughlin accused the
OL,19,Fminister and her party of being
OL,20,F"totally inconsistent" on the issue.
