OL,7,FDuring Assembly question time, Foyle
OL,8,FMLA Ms McLaughlin had called on Ms
OL,9,FArchibald to rule out a rise in the
OL,10,Ffee cap in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FWhen the minister declined to do so,
OL,13,Fthe SDLP representative highlighted
OL,14,Fthat Sinn Fein is campaigning for fees
OL,15,Fto be abolished in the Republic of
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,18,F"You should be consistent with your
OL,19,Fposition on tuition fees," she told
OL,20,Fthe minister.
