OL,4,Chas 'partitionist' stance on tuition
OL,5,Cfees
OL,7,F"In the south, you want to reduce and
OL,8,Fabolish tuition fees, and in the north
OL,9,Fyou're not ruling out raising them.
OL,10,FThis is totally inconsistent. And for
OL,11,Fan all-island party, you're acting in
OL,12,Fa very partitionist manner.
OL,14,F"Are you really telling this House
OL,15,Fthat Sinn Fein are happy with two
OL,16,Fdifferent policy positions in relation
OL,17,Fto tuition fees north and south? The
OL,18,Fvalue of a student in the south is
OL,19,Fgreater than in the north?"
