OL,7,FThe minister, whose department has
OL,8,Fresponsibility for funding the higher
OL,9,Feducation sector in Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Fdefended her party's position.
OL,12,F"Let me say that, from my perspective,
OL,13,Fideally, student fees would be zero,
OL,14,Fbut we have to work within the
OL,15,Ffinancial reality that we have," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
