OL,5,Cfees
OL,7,F"And obviously the system that we
OL,8,Fhave, which is imposed upon us by the
OL,9,FBritish Government in respect of their
OL,10,Fpolicy in relation to fees and years
OL,11,Fof austerity, has had an impact on all
OL,12,Fof our public services, including our
OL,13,Funiversities, which are a key economic
OL,14,Fdriver.
OL,16,F"So we need to ensure fees are at a
OL,17,Flevel that is affordable for students
OL,18,Fand maintains the financial viability
OL,19,Fof universities.
