OL,7,FLast week, the heads of Queen's
OL,8,FUniversity, Ulster University and the
OL,9,FOpen University in Ireland co-signed a
OL,10,Fletter to the five largest parties at
OL,11,FStormont to warn the current funding
OL,12,Farrangements are "not sustainable".
OL,14,FThe three leaders acknowledged that
OL,15,Fany increase in tuition fees agreed by
OL,16,FStormont should not be seen in
OL,17,F"isolation" and they also expressed
OL,18,Fsupport for a corresponding rise in
OL,19,Fthe maintenance grant available to
OL,20,Fstudents from low-income households.
